title: I Snuck Into My Mayor Rival's Head Quarters With A Gift | Ep.5
description: In this video, Max Fosh sneaks into his mayor rival's headquarters with a gift as part of his ongoing campaign. He manages to pull off the prank without getting caught.
summary: Max Fosh sneaks into his mayor rival's headquarters with a gift as part of his campaign antics.
